Maintainer: Oystein Sorensen <oystein.sorensen.1985@gmail.com>
Description: Estimation of Mallows' rank model using the SMC2 algorithm
    (Chopin et al. (2013) <doi:10.1111/j.1467-9868.2012.01046.x>). Supports data
    in the form of complete and partial rankings, and pairwise preferences.
